window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>Fated mates. Unbreakable bonds. Love that defies the odds.</i></b></p> <p>Welcome to Otter Cove, Alaska, a remote shifter haven where primal instincts reign, danger lurks in the shadows, and destiny refuses to be ignored. This complete collection brings together nine thrilling paranormal romances, each filled with fierce alphas, resilient heroines, and the kind of passion that burns as wild as the Alaskan wilderness.</p> <p>From runaway brides and unexpected rescues to high-stakes conspiracies and holiday magic, every story is a pulse-pounding journey of love, survival, and the undeniable power of fate.</p> <p>Escape into the world of Otter Cove, where shifters fight for their mates, challenges forge unbreakable love, and happily ever afters are anything but ordinary.</p>"; 
